Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Divorced?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.85,0:00:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll apparently be shipping off to Tokyo later this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off to Tokyo...? You're going to transfer schools?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have one more year until I graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And college entrance exams are coming up, so she said it would be okay if I stayed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, though, I'll still be going to college there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... don't scare me like that, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Less talking, more eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll be done soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey runts, what are you doing today on your day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.05,0:00:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice skating.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masa, leave after you've cleaned your dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masa, it's gonna get dark out if you're this slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get your stuff ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you the one who suggested staying behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking whether or not you told your mom you wanted to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess... but she was the one who said it'd be fine to stay if I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I said, "Oh... okay."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've thought a lot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I haven't...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's no way I could go with my girlfriend still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... I thought I'd tell you today, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I confessed my feelings to Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:13.86,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:19.82,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:25.95,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:31.92,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:39.30,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:44.01,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:49.94,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:58.82,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:03.74,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:10.87,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:17.63,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:13.86,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:19.82,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:25.95,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:31.92,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:39.30,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:44.01,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:49.94,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:58.82,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:03.74,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:10.87,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:17.63,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:33.06,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1100)\fscx113.75\fscy103\pos(159,377)}Episode 23 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I was sick in bed, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I tend to be good at playing dirty, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to ask how she responded?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm going home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't jump to conclusions...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't confessed, do you really think two guys would go ice skating on a Sunday morning like this--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've known each other since the sixth grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate that, moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're back already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as I told him that I confessed to Takahashi, he went blue in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me say something... I think you already know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:05:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're not under the impression that it went well, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So little has changed between us that it's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she didn't refuse you, did she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How... did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've always only taken challenges when the odds are in your favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see now. I can understand why Moto would get so upset about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? How'd you handle yourself in this little challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... can make you happier than he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect you, Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, don't give me your answer right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend to accept any answer but "yes."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not taking this lightly, and I'm not confessing just for the hell of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you refuse me, it won't stop me from loving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I've decided to live with and accept these feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why... I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it ever gets hard on you, or you can't bear with it any longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...remember that I'm here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... I'll always be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeuchi-kun told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to give me your answer right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness he said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to hurt him... and in the first place, it's just impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizu-chin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, have you made up with Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But didn't you go to see him when he was sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I didn't end up going in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you haven't gotten in touch with him at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning on doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizu-chin, I don't know... my head's so mixed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... it's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I might not be the right girl for Yano after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand his feelings at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I planned on giving it all my effort, but I keep on giving up at some point...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I feel awful about giving up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I end up blaming it on Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must be such horrible girlfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All relationships are like this. Don't blame yourself so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Takeuchi-kun said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, when you see him at school tomorrow, be sure to kiss and make up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and like Yamamoto-san said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'll never be able to understand Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm pessimistic about it, it's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm pessimistic about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:13.42,tab.,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(280,109)\frz22.583}Gym Class: Snow Shoveling
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks! It's so cold out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gym class first thing on first day of the week... we're so unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna put on extra clothes for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, good morning--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I ignored him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm not being sarcastic or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I was miserable that my girlfriend didn't come to see me the three days I was out sick or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I have such a big...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so it's begun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, don't play tag!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared to talk to Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a grip already! Don't make me feel worse than I already do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got over a cold... geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's different from what you just said...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys have their outward appearance, and they have their real feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand? Everything I'm about to say are my real feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was incredibly lonely when you didn't come to visit, call, or even send a text message.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how angry you may have been, that was just cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It made me feel miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I was no better than a flea or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I hate playing tag, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a grip and talk to me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... talk to me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yeah. I'm sorry, too..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could just say that, we'd be back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi... don't you want to make up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano... are you sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you really don't think I'm no good as a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...aren't you exhausted from going out with me already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm not confident..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not right... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure we're really meant for each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you want someone who can...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I can understand him a whole lot more than you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...understand you differently than I can?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely going to say no, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will he deny it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to, isn't he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone... who can understand me differently than you can?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying someone else would be better for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep saying things... that only make me more uneasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...deal with this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't we do something so easy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it just so easy that it seems hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motoharu, could you help me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ground's frozen, and I can't get the shovel in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we're out of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:15:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then in the spring, could you dig up those seedlings and send them to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're pretty bad at planning things, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You planted a ton of rose seedlings in the spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but left putting them in pots until the ground froze over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you really been thinking about this divorce for a year now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help it. Gardening is the only thing I take pleasure in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you only think of things impulsively.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you want something, you get it without thinking of the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your marriage gets jumbled, whether or not to get divorce gets jumbled, digging things up gets jumbled...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a big nuisance, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't give birth to you impulsively.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking about the saplings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you were thinking of growing those on the veranda? Are you dumb?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! The thorns hurt like hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I've just been a little on edge since this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just seems like you're always blaming me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never blamed you for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I said I wanted to get married, you followed me without saying a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found someone I want to marry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without once complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it will make you happy, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be my guilty conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better be happy this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave birth to you on a whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I not surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an unexpected pregnancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had never once thought of wanting a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was also scared of aborting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then I thought, maybe if I gave birth...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that man would consider divorcing his wife. That much is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it didn't work out that well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course. You're the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Everything's always either hit or miss with me, and unplanned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No forethought to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I do or achieve, it always ends up failure. As a woman and a mother, I'm the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't thought of becoming happy, this late in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you getting divorced?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can really stand on my own two feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forty-two. Got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... there is one thing I did succeed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I thought I had messed up at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just so unexpected at the time, and I regretted it severely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motoharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I gave birth to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, I'm grateful that I was just a girl who never thought ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've given me enough happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't wish for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty interesting. Wanna take a look, Nana?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I borrow it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi. What are your plans for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have no other plans, want to go home together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go home by myself today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nana...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is what all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you leave it like this, you two will really break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I talked with him now, we'll only go further in the wrong direction...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, but because you're having such a hard time, you need to take that step.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, you spend too much time on those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought this for a while, but even though Yano's chasing you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...do you really think he'll chase you forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you disconnect from Yano's feelings now, it'll be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think he'll chase you forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizu-chin's words keep echoing in my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you disconnect from Yano's feelings now, it'll be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.42,0:22:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I take back what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take back what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.93,0:22:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words I said two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.31,0:22:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I said that you only used me to get revenge on my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.90,0:23:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't do it for revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.15,0:23:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it out of sympathy for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, there's no changing the fact that it was the worst thing we could've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:41.23,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Ima kimi ga iikaketa kotoba ga
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.23,0:23:47.40,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Yubisaki ni sotto oritekita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.40,0:23:54.03,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanimo iwanakute ii yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:59.91,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumaida yubi wo gyutto atatamete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:16.35,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotoba wa kotoba dakara kokoro hanbun mo tsutaenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.35,0:24:28.99,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Setsunakute modokashikute yuuyake futari wo tsutsundeiru
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.99,0:24:42.29,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Komiageru mune no omoi kokoro ga itai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.63,0:24:59.22,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Setsunakute modokashikute kaerenai kono mama aruiteitai
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.22,0:25:14.95,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Yabaisaki ni kanjiteiru kokoro no kotoba wo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:41.23,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The words you were just about to say
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.23,0:23:47.40,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,fell softly onto my fingertips.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.40,0:23:54.03,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:59.91,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clasp your hand tightly and warm it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:16.35,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Because words are words, I can't express half of the feelings in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.35,0:24:28.99,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so wrenching and irritating as the sunset engulfs the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.99,0:24:42.29,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart aches from all the feelings welling up inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.63,0:24:59.22,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so wrenching and irritating that I can't go home. I want to keep walking like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.22,0:25:14.95,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the words from your heart on my fingertips.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.93,0:25:34.99,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFE6FE&\3c&HD868E0&\pos(437,373)\fscx107.5\fscy123.75}Episode 24 Preview...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.40,0:25:10.69,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you actually thinking\N of going with your mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.44,0:25:14.86,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to keep\N giving you those chances?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.86,0:25:16.37,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,With women, if you're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.37,0:25:19.08,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,...by their side, you don't\N know where they'll run off to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.08,0:25:22.45,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of this regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.45,0:25:27.79,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...\N He seriously might go...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.79,0:25:31.96,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano's... going to leave?
